  Localised strings для spec 008 (bidirectional-config-sync) UI components.

  Naming convention per ADR-004 + ux-quality CHK-008/009:
    config_sync_indicator_*   — PushIndicator visual states (FR-015 + SC-001b)
    config_sync_banner_*      — PendingBanner texts (FR-047)
    config_sync_dialog_*      — DiscardConfirmDialog (FR-057)
    config_sync_badge_*       — PendingBadge (FR-046)
    config_sync_merge_*       — MergeScreen (FR-050..054)

  Wording principle per elderly-friendly CHK-009 fix:
   - No developer jargon: never «push», «сервер», «pending» в user-visible text.
   - No persona terms: never «бабушка», «admin», «managed».
   - Neutral plain Russian; technical concepts paraphrased.

  Russian-first per project audience.
-->
